    \n    \n        \n                \n                    \n                        \n                                    \u003cdiv id=\"article-body\" itemprop=\"articleBody\"\u003e\u003cp\u003eCarriers offering freebies is nothing new â€” T-Mobile was recently seen giving away a \u003ca href=\"https://www.androidpolice.com/t-mobile-tuesdays-free-doordash-dashpass/\" target=\"_blank\"\u003efree year of DashPass\u003c/a\u003e to its customers. But if you\u0026#39;re a Verizon customer, you might want to act fast, as the company is giving out free Amazon gift cards.\u003c/p\u003e    \u003cp\u003eEarlier today, \u003ca href=\"https://www.androidpolice.com/verizon-app-customer-service-upgrades/\" target=\"_blank\"\u003eVerizon announced\u003c/a\u003e an overhaul of its customer support system, integrating AI across the entire vertical. To celebrate, it seems the company is giving away free Amazon gift cards worth $5 and $20.\u003c/p\u003e            \n    \n                    \n                        \n    \n    \n                                        \n    \n        \n    \n        \n                \n        \n    \u003cdiv data-include-community-rating=\"false\" id=\"d516-477e-96a180d11fa0\" data-nosnippet=\"\"\u003e\n        \n        \n                        \t\n\t                \n\t\t\u003ca href=\"https://www.androidpolice.com/verizon-high-yield-savings-account-release/\"\u003e\n\t\n\t\u003cdiv data-img-url=\"https://static1.anpoimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/wm/2024/02/verizon-myplan-unlimited-plus-on-phone.jpg\" data-modal-id=\"single-image-modal\" data-modal-container-id=\"single-image-modal-container\" data-img-caption=\"\u0026#34;\u0026#34;\"\u003e\n\n            \n\n\n\n\n\u003cfigure\u003e\n        \u003cpicture\u003e\n        \n                                        \n                                    \n                                                                                                                                                                            \n            \n                                                \n                        \n            \n            \n                                        \n                                        \u003csource media=\"(min-width: 1024px)\" data-srcset=\"https://static1.anpoimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/wm/2024/02/verizon-myplan-unlimited-plus-on-phone.jpg?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=422\u0026amp;h=268\u0026amp;dpr=2\" srcset=\"https://static1.anpoimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/wm/2024/02/verizon-myplan-unlimited-plus-on-phone.jpg?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=422\u0026amp;h=268\u0026amp;dpr=2\"/\u003e\n                    \n                                        \n                                    \n                                                                                                                                                                            \n            \n                                                \n                        \n            \n            \n                                        \n                                        \u003csource media=\"(min-width: 768px)\" data-srcset=\"https://static1.anpoimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/wm/2024/02/verizon-myplan-unlimited-plus-on-phone.jpg?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=310\u0026amp;h=220\u0026amp;dpr=2\" srcset=\"https://static1.anpoimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/wm/2024/02/verizon-myplan-unlimited-plus-on-phone.jpg?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=310\u0026amp;h=220\u0026amp;dpr=2\"/\u003e\n                    \n                                        \n                                    \n                                                                                                                                                                            \n            \n                                                \n                        \n            \n            \n                                        \n                                        \u003csource media=\"(min-width: 481px)\" data-srcset=\"https://static1.anpoimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/wm/2024/02/verizon-myplan-unlimited-plus-on-phone.jpg?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=720\u0026amp;h=400\u0026amp;dpr=2\" srcset=\"https://static1.anpoimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/wm/2024/02/verizon-myplan-unlimited-plus-on-phone.jpg?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=720\u0026amp;h=400\u0026amp;dpr=2\"/\u003e\n                    \n                                        \n                                    \n                                                                                                                                                                            \n            \n                                                \n                        \n            \n            \n                                        \n                                        \u003csource media=\"(min-width: 0px)\" data-srcset=\"https://static1.anpoimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/wm/2024/02/verizon-myplan-unlimited-plus-on-phone.jpg?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=432\u0026amp;h=260\u0026amp;dpr=2\" srcset=\"https://static1.anpoimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/wm/2024/02/verizon-myplan-unlimited-plus-on-phone.jpg?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=432\u0026amp;h=260\u0026amp;dpr=2\"/\u003e\n                    \n                    \u003cimg width=\"4032\" height=\"3024\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" alt=\"Verizon myPlan Unlimited Plus on a Galaxy phone\" data-img-url=\"https://static1.anpoimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/wm/2024/02/verizon-myplan-unlimited-plus-on-phone.jpg\" src=\"https://static1.anpoimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/wm/2024/02/verizon-myplan-unlimited-plus-on-phone.jpg\"/\u003e\n        \n    \u003c/picture\u003e\n                \n    \u003c/figure\u003e\n\n\n        \u003c/div\u003e\n\n\t\t\u003c/a\u003e\n\t\n\n        \n                    \u003cp\u003e\u003cspan data-field=\"label\"\u003eRelated\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n                \n        \n        \n        \n            \u003c/div\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eTo claim the offer, head to the new My Verizon app. In the app, go to the \u0026#34;\u003cstrong\u003eMe\u003c/strong\u003e\u0026#34; section, then to \u0026#34;\u003cstrong\u003emyAccess\u003c/strong\u003e\u0026#34;, and under that select \u0026#34;\u003cstrong\u003eMy savings \u0026amp; benefits\u003c/strong\u003e.\u0026#34; In the \u0026#34;\u003cstrong\u003eFeatured Rewards\u003c/strong\u003e\u0026#34; section, you should see a banner for a free Amazon gift card. Tap it to claim your gift card.\u003c/p\u003e    \u003cp\u003eOnce claimed, go back to the \u0026#34;\u003cstrong\u003emyAccess\u003c/strong\u003e\u0026#34; page and then to \u0026#34;\u003cstrong\u003eClaimed deals and more\u003c/strong\u003e\u0026#34; to find your gift card. You can redeem it directly from there by hitting the Redeem button, or you can manually redeem it by going to Amazon\u0026#39;s website or app.\u003c/p\u003e    \u003ch2 id=\"you-can-snag-a-free-amazon-gift-card-from-verizon-right-now\"\u003e\n                        You can snag a free Amazon gift card from Verizon right now\n               \u003c/h2\u003e\n                \n    \n    \n    \n                \n    \n                \n        \n                                                            \n                                                                                                                        \n                            \n    \n    \n    \n    \n    \u003cdiv data-img-url=\"https://static1.anpoimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/verizon-free-amazon-gift-card.jpg\" data-img-desc=\"\u0026#34;Via: \u0026lt;a href=\\\u0026#34;https:\\/\\/www.droid-life.com\\/2025\\/06\\/24\\/verizon-is-giving-out-free-amazon-gift-cards\\/\\\u0026#34; rel=\\\u0026#34;noopener noreferrer nofollow\\\u0026#34; target=\\\u0026#34;_blank\\\u0026#34;\u0026gt;PhoneArena\u0026lt;\\/a\u0026gt;\u0026#34;\" data-modal-id=\"single-image-modal\" data-modal-container-id=\"single-image-modal-container\" data-img-caption=\"\u0026#34;\u0026#34;\"\u003e\n\n            \n\n\n\n\n\u003cfigure\u003e\n        \u003cpicture\u003e\n        \n                                        \n                                    \n                                                                                                                                                                            \n            \n                                                \n                        \n            \n            \n                                        \n                                        \u003csource media=\"(min-width: 1024px)\" data-srcset=\"https://static1.anpoimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/verizon-free-amazon-gift-card.jpg?q=70\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=825\u0026amp;dpr=1\" srcset=\"https://static1.anpoimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/verizon-free-amazon-gift-card.jpg?q=70\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=825\u0026amp;dpr=1\"/\u003e\n                    \n                                        \n                                    \n                                                                                                                                                                            \n            \n                                                \n                        \n            \n            \n                                        \n                                        \u003csource media=\"(min-width: 768px)\" data-srcset=\"https://static1.anpoimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/verizon-free-amazon-gift-card.jpg?q=70\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=825\u0026amp;dpr=1\" srcset=\"https://static1.anpoimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/verizon-free-amazon-gift-card.jpg?q=70\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=825\u0026amp;dpr=1\"/\u003e\n                    \n                                        \n                                    \n                                                                                                                                                                            \n            \n                                                \n                        \n            \n            \n                                        \n                                        \u003csource media=\"(min-width: 481px)\" data-srcset=\"https://static1.anpoimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/verizon-free-amazon-gift-card.jpg?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=800\u0026amp;dpr=2\" srcset=\"https://static1.anpoimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/verizon-free-amazon-gift-card.jpg?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=800\u0026amp;dpr=2\"/\u003e\n                    \n                                        \n                                    \n                                                                                                                                                                            \n            \n                                                \n                        \n            \n            \n                                        \n                                        \u003csource media=\"(min-width: 0px)\" data-srcset=\"https://static1.anpoimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/verizon-free-amazon-gift-card.jpg?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=500\u0026amp;dpr=2\" srcset=\"https://static1.anpoimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/verizon-free-amazon-gift-card.jpg?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=500\u0026amp;dpr=2\"/\u003e\n                    \n                    \u003cimg width=\"1600\" height=\"1400\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" alt=\"Amazon free gift card in Verizon app\" data-img-url=\"https://static1.anpoimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/verizon-free-amazon-gift-card.jpg\" src=\"https://static1.anpoimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/verizon-free-amazon-gift-card.jpg\"/\u003e\n        \n    \u003c/picture\u003e\n                                    \n    \u003c/figure\u003e\n\n\n        \u003c/div\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eThe page notes that gift cards are available for a limited time or until supplies run out. According to some \u003ca href=\"https://www.reddit.com/r/verizon/comments/1lj8jz0/20_amazon_gift_card_in_my_access/\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer nofollow\" target=\"_blank\"\u003eReddit users\u003c/a\u003e, the $20 gift cards are already gone, but $5 gift cards are still being claimed.\u003c/p\u003e    \u003cp\u003e$5 might not sound like much, but free money is free, especially with \u003ca href=\"https://www.androidpolice.com/amazon-prime-day-2025-summer-event-july-8-to-july-11/\" target=\"_blank\"\u003ePrime Day coming up\u003c/a\u003e, where you can stack this with already discounted deals.\u003c/p\u003e    \u003cp\u003eVerizon hasn\u0026#39;t been known for freebies like T-Mobile, which runs the \u003ca href=\"https://www.androidpolice.com/t-mobile-tuesdays-9-year-anniversary/\" target=\"_blank\"\u003eT-Mobile Tuesdays\u003c/a\u003e program, offering weekly perks and discounts. But this could be a start. The company seems to be trying to retain customers with the new myAccess perks, especially since it\u0026#39;s been \u003ca href=\"https://www.androidpolice.com/verizon-is-losing-customers-left-and-right/\" target=\"_blank\"\u003elosing a lot of users\u003c/a\u003e this year.\u003c/p\u003e    \n    \n    \n    \n\u003c/div\u003e\n    \n                \n        \n        \n\n\n        \n\n\n\n\n\n                \n    \u003c/article\u003e\n\n    \n            \n        \u003c/div\u003e\u003c/div\u003e",
